WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:10.427 --> 00:00:11.636
I'm going…

2
00:00:12.554 --> 00:00:13.555
Nanami.

3
00:00:13.638 --> 00:00:15.140
I won't allow it.

4
00:00:15.223 --> 00:00:17.934
I told you the reason this morning.

5
00:00:19.144 --> 00:00:21.396
Now that they have put on the Veil.

6
00:00:21.479 --> 00:00:26.526
he's probably still alive
and in Satozakura High School now.

7
00:00:29.612 --> 00:00:33.908
I'll come right away.
Please be on standby. Itadori.

8
00:00:36.995 --> 00:00:39.039
I guess it's useless to say that.

9
00:00:41.041 --> 00:00:44.461
That's all.
I'll leave the rest to you. Ino.

10
00:00:44.544 --> 00:00:45.378
What?

11
00:00:46.629 --> 00:00:48.423
Is there a problem?

12
00:00:48.506 --> 00:00:51.426
No. but their numbers…

13
00:00:52.135 --> 00:00:53.803
There are too many of them.

14
00:00:54.637 --> 00:00:56.431
And they are all humans. right?

15
00:00:57.057 --> 00:01:01.770
I can recommend you to become
a Grade 1 Jujutsu Sorcerer.

16
00:01:05.732 --> 00:01:08.109
I'll do my best!

17
00:01:08.193 --> 00:01:10.653
All right!

18
00:01:13.698 --> 00:01:15.742
Step aside. Mr. Ijichi.

19
00:01:16.951 --> 00:01:19.621
Our job is to save people.

20
00:01:20.121 --> 00:01:23.625
That includes you. the students.

21
00:01:25.376 --> 00:01:28.421
I won't make the same mistake again.

22
00:01:30.381 --> 00:01:33.259
You can't go. Itadori.

23
00:01:36.638 --> 00:01:38.765
I'm sorry. Mr. Ijichi.

24
00:01:46.606 --> 00:01:49.818
What are you doing. Junpei?

25
00:01:52.821 --> 00:01:55.532
Step aside. Jujutsu Sorcerer.

26
00:03:37.175 --> 00:03:38.218
Moon Dregs!

27
00:03:44.474 --> 00:03:46.517
Jellyfish Shikigami?

28
00:03:46.601 --> 00:03:49.646
My attacks don't work
after he goes inside it!

29
00:03:51.022 --> 00:03:52.523
I'll repeat myself.

30
00:03:52.607 --> 00:03:54.734
Step aside. Jujutsu Sorcerer.

31
00:03:55.485 --> 00:03:57.237
This has nothing to do with you.

32
00:03:57.737 --> 00:04:00.281
That's not for you to decide!

33
00:04:00.782 --> 00:04:05.119
What's the point
of randomly saving people?

34
00:04:06.621 --> 00:04:08.456
Don't mistake…

35
00:04:08.539 --> 00:04:10.333
the value of life!

36
00:04:14.170 --> 00:04:18.508
The heart.
the so-called compassion by human beings.

37
00:04:18.591 --> 00:04:22.220
is just the metabolism of the soul.
and it's an illusion!

38
00:04:22.720 --> 00:04:25.807
Don't use illusive rules to restrain me.

39
00:04:26.432 --> 00:04:29.727
Those who deserve to die
shouldn't be spared.

40
00:04:29.811 --> 00:04:31.187
You have no right to stop me.

41
00:04:32.230 --> 00:04:33.773
Just sleep in there.

42
00:04:34.315 --> 00:04:36.276
I have work to do.

43
00:04:39.862 --> 00:04:41.614
Your cursed technique…

44
00:04:42.115 --> 00:04:43.324
is poison.

45
00:04:44.826 --> 00:04:46.995
The poison extracted
from your cursed energy

46
00:04:47.078 --> 00:04:49.622
is secreted through
the tentacles of Shikigami.

47
00:04:49.706 --> 00:04:53.584
The toxicity level. size. and strength
of the Shikigami can be changed.

48
00:04:53.668 --> 00:04:55.086
Just take your time to learn.

49
00:04:56.546 --> 00:04:59.549
It usually takes years for
Jujutsu Sorcerers to learn that skill.

50
00:04:59.632 --> 00:05:03.136
but I can teach you.
so you'll be able to fight soon.

51
00:05:04.804 --> 00:05:07.098
Junpei. you're truly talented.

52
00:05:10.143 --> 00:05:12.979
Who are you making excuses for?

53
00:05:33.541 --> 00:05:34.834
Why?

54
00:05:35.335 --> 00:05:37.462
Moon Dregs' poison is ineffective on him!

55
00:05:46.095 --> 00:05:48.181
Why must you hinder me?

56
00:05:48.264 --> 00:05:49.098
Why…

57
00:05:49.932 --> 00:05:51.225
Why…

58
00:05:52.477 --> 00:05:53.853
Why?

59
00:05:59.859 --> 00:06:02.361
He can't move in the air.

60
00:06:02.862 --> 00:06:06.032
If I want to crush him. I need to
strike him while he is in mid-air!

61
00:06:16.125 --> 00:06:18.503
I don't understand a single thing…

62
00:06:20.338 --> 00:06:22.465
you're saying. Junpei!

63
00:06:23.841 --> 00:06:26.302
Even if you said something
that quite makes sense.

64
00:06:27.678 --> 00:06:31.182
The best way to beat a Shikigami
is to go for the user.

65
00:06:32.475 --> 00:06:33.601
You just…

66
00:06:36.979 --> 00:06:39.774
want to think that you're right.

67
00:06:45.279 --> 00:06:46.989
I don't know your motives.

68
00:06:47.073 --> 00:06:48.950
You must have had a reason.

69
00:06:50.201 --> 00:06:51.035
However…

70
00:06:51.119 --> 00:06:53.121
Is it really…

71
00:06:53.746 --> 00:06:56.415
worth giving up that kind of life?

72
00:07:00.169 --> 00:07:02.713
You said the human heart is illusive.

73
00:07:03.256 --> 00:07:05.758
But could you say that to your mother?

74
00:07:07.093 --> 00:07:10.346
People don't have hearts…

75
00:07:10.430 --> 00:07:12.140
-You're still…
-They don't!

76
00:07:13.516 --> 00:07:14.809
Otherwise…

77
00:07:16.519 --> 00:07:17.728
Otherwise…

78
00:07:18.271 --> 00:07:20.022
Are you saying that my mother and I

79
00:07:20.523 --> 00:07:23.359
have been cursed by people with hearts?

80
00:07:25.403 --> 00:07:28.239
That's too much.

81
00:07:28.739 --> 00:07:34.495
I no longer know what's right and wrong.

82
00:07:42.962 --> 00:07:44.172
Why…

83
00:07:46.591 --> 00:07:48.176
Why didn't you evade it?

84
00:07:52.889 --> 00:07:54.098
I'm sorry.

85
00:07:54.765 --> 00:07:58.561
I didn't know anything.
but I said those things.

86
00:08:03.232 --> 00:08:05.109
Tell me what happened.

87
00:08:06.527 --> 00:08:10.406
I'll never curse you. Junpei.

88
00:08:11.657 --> 00:08:12.742
So…

89
00:08:20.041 --> 00:08:22.877
How could this be? Your mother…

90
00:08:29.217 --> 00:08:31.969
Junpei. come to Jujutsu High.

91
00:08:32.678 --> 00:08:34.889
We have very strong teachers

92
00:08:35.389 --> 00:08:37.850
and plenty of reliable comrades.

93
00:08:39.393 --> 00:08:40.978
If we work together.

94
00:08:41.479 --> 00:08:45.024
we can find the culprit
who cursed your mother.

95
00:08:45.650 --> 00:08:48.110
We will avenge her!

96
00:08:49.195 --> 00:08:50.655
Let's fight together!

97
00:08:53.950 --> 00:08:54.825
What?

98
00:08:56.285 --> 00:08:57.245
Who are you?

99
00:08:59.038 --> 00:09:00.581
What's with this guy?

100
00:09:02.124 --> 00:09:03.459
Is he a human?

101
00:09:04.043 --> 00:09:05.836
Nice to meet you.

102
00:09:06.420 --> 00:09:08.839
No. this sensation…

103
00:09:08.923 --> 00:09:10.800
Sukuna's vessel.

104
00:09:12.802 --> 00:09:14.178
Wait. Mahito!

105
00:09:18.516 --> 00:09:19.934
Am I an idiot?

106
00:09:20.017 --> 00:09:22.353
A human-looking Cursed Spirit
with a patchwork face…

107
00:09:22.436 --> 00:09:25.356
It's exactly the Cursed Spirit
that Nanami described!

108
00:09:25.940 --> 00:09:27.400
Run. Junpei!

109
00:09:28.067 --> 00:09:30.611
I don't know what
your relationship is with him.

110
00:09:30.695 --> 00:09:33.322
but run away now!

111
00:09:33.406 --> 00:09:34.407
Please!

112
00:09:34.991 --> 00:09:36.701
Calm down. Itadori.

113
00:09:37.243 --> 00:09:38.953
Mahito is not…

114
00:09:45.293 --> 00:09:47.712
A bad person.

115
00:09:52.592 --> 00:09:56.012
You know you're smart. right. Junpei?

116
00:09:57.513 --> 00:10:00.725
But sometimes. deliberation
can lead to more serious consequences

117
00:10:00.808 --> 00:10:02.393
than rash actions.

118
00:10:03.019 --> 00:10:05.021
You're the typical example.

119
00:10:06.272 --> 00:10:09.817
You're just as stupid as those

120
00:10:10.318 --> 00:10:12.737
you looked down on.

121
00:10:15.072 --> 00:10:17.491
And that's why you'll die.

122
00:10:19.076 --> 00:10:21.120
Idle Transfiguration.

123
00:10:30.338 --> 00:10:33.758
Come on. let's begin the second round!

124
00:10:34.342 --> 00:10:35.509
Junpei…

125
00:10:37.928 --> 00:10:39.180
Junpei!

126
00:10:40.014 --> 00:10:41.599
Snap out of it!

127
00:10:41.682 --> 00:10:43.434
I'll treat you now.

128
00:10:49.357 --> 00:10:50.483
Sukuna…

129
00:10:52.026 --> 00:10:53.861
Sukuna!

130
00:10:55.196 --> 00:10:56.280
What is it?

131
00:10:57.865 --> 00:10:59.450
I'll do anything!

132
00:10:59.533 --> 00:11:01.369
Do whatever you want with me!

133
00:11:01.452 --> 00:11:04.622
So please heal Junpei like how you…

134
00:11:04.705 --> 00:11:06.832
cured my heart back then!

135
00:11:07.875 --> 00:11:09.377
I refuse.

136
00:11:14.048 --> 00:11:15.716
Darn you.

137
00:11:18.552 --> 00:11:22.807
Good. He has forgotten
about our Binding Vow.

138
00:11:24.683 --> 00:11:26.519
I'm so happy!

139
00:11:26.602 --> 00:11:32.566
You gave up your pride and future.
You gave up everything to beg me.

140
00:11:34.068 --> 00:11:36.612
But you can't save anything.

141
00:11:36.695 --> 00:11:38.823
He rejected the Binding Vow?

142
00:11:39.532 --> 00:11:44.203
Although souls can't use
Reverse Cursed Technique to heal…

143
00:11:45.871 --> 00:11:48.207
Is he not good at treating others?

144
00:11:49.208 --> 00:11:50.626
You're so miserable.

145
00:11:50.709 --> 00:11:53.754
You're so miserable. brat.

146
00:11:55.548 --> 00:11:59.093
But this is just
the first step towards my goal. anyway.

147
00:11:59.176 --> 00:12:00.928
This is pretty good too.

148
00:12:18.529 --> 00:12:20.698
Oh. I see.

149
00:12:21.323 --> 00:12:22.283
In the end.

150
00:12:22.950 --> 00:12:24.452
they are nothing…

151
00:12:25.619 --> 00:12:27.037
but evil curses.

152
00:12:31.250 --> 00:12:34.628
Yuji…

153
00:12:42.511 --> 00:12:44.930
Why?

154
00:13:12.791 --> 00:13:13.918
He's dead already?

155
00:13:14.502 --> 00:13:17.546
I did transfigure him
a little too violently. after all.

156
00:13:20.132 --> 00:13:21.759
No wonder he's dead.

157
00:13:25.596 --> 00:13:27.348
That's some kind of strange attack.

158
00:13:27.431 --> 00:13:28.682
Interesting!

159
00:13:28.766 --> 00:13:31.268
Unfortunately. it doesn't work.

160
00:13:31.352 --> 00:13:33.646
As long as I maintain
the shape of my soul…

161
00:13:34.313 --> 00:13:35.314
What?

162
00:13:37.733 --> 00:13:39.360
What's happening?

163
00:13:42.279 --> 00:13:45.032
Even my soul got beaten up.

164
00:13:46.617 --> 00:13:47.868
Oh. right.

165
00:13:47.952 --> 00:13:50.621
Yuji Itadori is a vessel.

166
00:13:50.704 --> 00:13:55.209
There is another soul
that dwells inside his body.

167
00:13:56.001 --> 00:13:57.628
So naturally…

168
00:13:58.837 --> 00:14:00.548
Can you perceive it?

169
00:14:01.549 --> 00:14:03.509
The contours of my soul. that is!

170
00:14:10.766 --> 00:14:17.481
It's as if what I've said were all lies.

171
00:14:17.565 --> 00:14:19.650
My true intention is…

172
00:14:20.985 --> 00:14:23.112
I'll fucking kill you.

173
00:14:38.460 --> 00:14:41.130
Aren't you mistaking it for "exorcise"?

174
00:14:41.213 --> 00:14:42.506
Jujutsu Sorcerer.

175
00:14:45.676 --> 00:14:49.680
Yuji Itadori
has no regard for his own life.

176
00:14:49.763 --> 00:14:52.182
Geto doesn't allow me to use
an external Binding Vow

177
00:14:52.266 --> 00:14:54.560
such as taking hostages.

178
00:14:55.853 --> 00:15:00.441
Then if he meets someone he wants
to kill badly but is unable to.

179
00:15:00.524 --> 00:15:02.735
will he rely on Sukuna?

180
00:15:03.777 --> 00:15:05.613
If Junpei's death isn't enough.

181
00:15:05.696 --> 00:15:09.241
I'll just have to kill everyone
in this school.

182
00:15:09.909 --> 00:15:12.328
A hatred that transcends
his own interests will impose

183
00:15:12.411 --> 00:15:17.249
a Binding Vow on Yuji Itadori
in Sukuna's favor.

184
00:15:17.750 --> 00:15:22.129
It would be better if it increases
the chance of Sukuna joining us.

185
00:15:25.841 --> 00:15:30.512
But this means
I have to be stronger than him.

186
00:15:31.055 --> 00:15:32.598
And surprisingly. I'm up against…

187
00:15:33.682 --> 00:15:35.142
my mortal enemy.

188
00:15:54.536 --> 00:15:56.914
He keeps reshaping his soul.

189
00:15:56.997 --> 00:16:00.292
Should I not grapple him after a throw?

190
00:16:01.335 --> 00:16:03.587
Since his attack is effective.

191
00:16:03.671 --> 00:16:07.257
it's not a good idea to transform
my body to give him a bigger target.

192
00:16:08.592 --> 00:16:10.010
-In that case…
-In that case…

193
00:16:10.552 --> 00:16:13.305
I'll do it a hundred or thousand times.

194
00:16:14.473 --> 00:16:16.767
I'll continue to strike…

195
00:16:17.434 --> 00:16:19.520
until you're crushed!

196
00:16:20.771 --> 00:16:26.735
Let's change into
a streamlined form that's…

197
00:16:28.612 --> 00:16:29.863
optimal for killing!

198
00:16:55.973 --> 00:16:58.976
I'm sure you can't stretch forever.

199
00:17:16.744 --> 00:17:19.121
Normal people would have let go of it.

200
00:17:20.539 --> 00:17:22.666
If I extend my shape too wide.

201
00:17:22.750 --> 00:17:24.793
the operability
and strength will decrease.

202
00:17:49.818 --> 00:17:52.071
You can't beat me.

203
00:17:52.654 --> 00:17:54.490
Hurry up and switch.

204
00:17:56.283 --> 00:17:57.451
Switch to Sukuna.

205
00:17:59.578 --> 00:18:01.455
Idle Transfiguration.

206
00:18:09.505 --> 00:18:12.174
Did you just touch my soul?

207
00:18:12.674 --> 00:18:15.969
We both laughed at this brat
from the bottom of our hearts.

208
00:18:16.053 --> 00:18:17.679
I'll forgive you once.

209
00:18:18.722 --> 00:18:20.307
There's no second chance.

210
00:18:24.019 --> 00:18:25.729
Know your place…

211
00:18:27.606 --> 00:18:29.066
you fool.

212
00:18:35.114 --> 00:18:37.032
I'm not going to switch.

213
00:18:37.116 --> 00:18:38.575
I told you. didn't I?

214
00:18:40.744 --> 00:18:42.913
I'll fucking kill you.

215
00:19:18.407 --> 00:19:19.283
What?

216
00:19:26.582 --> 00:19:28.292
Oh. my.

217
00:19:28.876 --> 00:19:29.793
What?

218
00:19:31.086 --> 00:19:31.920
Nanami…

219
00:19:37.342 --> 00:19:38.844
I'll lecture you later.

220
00:19:39.511 --> 00:19:40.971
Report the situation first.

221
00:19:42.764 --> 00:19:45.767
I couldn't save them both.

222
00:19:46.602 --> 00:19:49.104
He's always thinking of others.

223
00:19:49.897 --> 00:19:52.316
How are you doing physically?

224
00:19:53.358 --> 00:19:54.776
I'm fine.

225
00:19:54.860 --> 00:19:56.945
I have a lot of holes. though.

226
00:19:57.905 --> 00:19:59.198
How is that fine?

227
00:19:59.698 --> 00:20:03.535
Also. everyone from the school
is unconscious in the gym.

228
00:20:04.494 --> 00:20:08.707
Hey. You look energetic. 7:3 Sorcerer.

229
00:20:09.374 --> 00:20:12.211
It's great that we're both doing well.

230
00:20:12.794 --> 00:20:14.421
Shall we hug…

231
00:20:15.214 --> 00:20:17.174
to celebrate our reunion?

232
00:20:23.138 --> 00:20:25.515
Itadori. why is his nose bleeding?

233
00:20:25.599 --> 00:20:26.642
What?

234
00:20:27.267 --> 00:20:28.810
I punched him.

235
00:20:28.894 --> 00:20:31.355
-When?
-At the very start.

236
00:20:31.438 --> 00:20:33.232
Did he touch you with his hand?

237
00:20:33.732 --> 00:20:34.608
Yes.

238
00:20:35.400 --> 00:20:38.111
My attacks have zero effect on him.

239
00:20:38.195 --> 00:20:40.113
What?

240
00:20:40.197 --> 00:20:42.824
-Why?
-The reason will come during the lecture.

241
00:20:43.700 --> 00:20:47.496
First. he may not be able
to use his ability on Itadori.

242
00:20:47.579 --> 00:20:50.707
Second. he has a reason
not to kill Itadori.

243
00:20:50.791 --> 00:20:53.001
Either way. it's an advantage.

244
00:20:53.502 --> 00:20:56.421
But I can stifle his movements.

245
00:20:57.673 --> 00:21:01.551
Let's create openings for each other
and take the opportunity to attack.

246
00:21:02.928 --> 00:21:05.472
We must exorcise him here.

247
00:21:07.891 --> 00:21:09.101
Okay!

248
00:22:41.026 --> 00:22:43.487
JUJU STROLL
